      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything i worked for... all those years in the lab. it was all based on a flawed premise. the data was misinterpreted, the whole theory is garbage. i've spent my entire life building a legacy that doesn't even exist. i'm just a fraud. there's nothing left of me now that the work is gone.",
